<div class="header">Confirm Your Job Alert Filter</div>

<h2>Hello!</h2>

<p>You've requested to receive job alerts for <strong><%= @job_alert_filter.category %> in <%= @job_alert_filter.region %></strong>.</p>

<p>To start receiving <strong><%= @job_alert_filter.frequency %></strong> email notifications about matching job opportunities, please confirm this filter by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @confirmation_url %>" class="button">Confirm This Job Alert Filter</a>
</div>

<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666;"><%= @confirmation_url %></p>

